message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to discuss the opportunity to purchase this valuable product from me. I believe it's a unique and high-quality item that will bring significant value to you. I'm willing to offer it to you for $750,000. This is a competitive price, considering the product's worth to you is $800,000. I think it's a great deal, and I'm confident you'll be happy with your decision. Let me know if you're interested!
